      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KISSES FOR RUBY (5) has a strong record here with 10 wins and 12 placings from 25 starts. Placed last time (30.13) at this track in a Other, finishing second and beaten 8 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. BUCKLE UP MAJEL (1) was narrowly beaten last time, jumping from this same box when a half a length second in a Grade 3/4 over 515m at this track. This tougher but expected to be in the finish. BUCKLE UP TAJA (8) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (30.10) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expected to feature again. PECO (2) scored by a nose last time (26.23) in a Other over 461m at Hobart. Has two wins already from this draw.",
